<div class="mystical-gradient min-h-screen py-8 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center py-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-4 drop-shadow-lg">
        <span class="shimmer-text">✨ 神秘の占い館 ✨</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-12 opacity-90">
        あなたの運命を紐解く、特別な占いの世界へようこそ
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🔮</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4">タロット占い</h3>
          <p class="mb-6 opacity-80">カードが示すあなたの未来</p>
          <%= link_to "占ってみる", "#", class: "inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-orange-500 text-white py-3 px-8 rounded-full font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg" %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">⭐</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4">星座占い</h3>
          <p class="mb-6 opacity-80">星々があなたに伝えるメッセージ</p>
          <%= link_to "占ってみる", "#", class: "inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-orange-500 text-white py-3 px-8 rounded-full font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg" %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🔢</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4">数秘術</h3>
          <p class="mb-6 opacity-80">数字に隠された運命の秘密</p>
          <%= link_to "占ってみる", "#", class: "inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-orange-500 text-white py-3 px-8 rounded-full font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/20 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6">今日のあなたの運勢</h2>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌟</div>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 opacity-90">
            今日は新しい出会いが待っています。直感を信じて行動することで、素晴らしい機会が訪れるでしょう。
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-lg">総合運:</span>
            <div class="text-2xl text-yellow-300">★★★★☆</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

 